Insider Activity


Individual




Joel L. Poppen



Mr. Joel L. Poppen is Secretary, VP-Legal Affairs & General Counsel at Micron Technology, Inc., a Member at The State Bar of Arizona, a Member at Idaho State Bar Association, and a Director at One Stone, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Micron Technology Foundation, Inc., Idaho Technology Council, and One Stone, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Illinois and a graduate degree from the Duke University School of Law.



